Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end
if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off
if bPartOfLayout then if GLOB_CONTEXT > 20 and GLOB_CONTEXT < 40 or gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then !! for Simple Model and in 3D Windoow if GLOB_CONTEXT > 20 and GLOB_CONTEXT < 40 then iResol = 3 else iResol = 12 endif else iResol = gs_resol * 3 endif else if GLOB_CONTEXT > 20 and GLOB_CONTEXT < 40 or gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then !! for Simple Model and in 3D Windoow iResol = 12 else iResol = gs_resol * 3 endif endif
! ====================================================================== ! TableTop ! ======================================================================
call "tableTops_m" parameters all gs_resol = iResol
resol iResol
if gs_leg_type_m = 0 then end
! ====================================================================== ! Legs ! ======================================================================
if gs_leg_type_m = 1 then legDistFromEdge = 0.06 leg_a = 0.025 leg_h = zzyzx - topThk - 0.01 endif if gs_leg_type_m = 2 then legDistFromEdge = 0.06 leg_a = 0.04 leg_h = zzyzx - topThk - 0.01 endif if gs_leg_type_m = 3 then legDistFromEdge = 0.035 + 0.06 leg_h = zzyzx - topThk - 0.09 endif if gs_leg_type_m = 4 then legDistFromEdge = 0.06 leg_h = zzyzx - topThk endif if gs_leg_type_m = 5 then legDistFromEdge = 0.015 leg_h = zzyzx - topThk endif if gs_leg_type_m = 6 then legDistFromEdge = 0.025 leg_h = zzyzx - topThk endif
leg_b = 0.04 * (gs_leg_type_m = 2)
if iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_90 or\ iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_135 or\ iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_180 or\ iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_360 or\ iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_P_TOP then gosub "legsForArchedDesks"
! ====================================================================== end ! ======================================================================
"legsForArchedDesks": if gs_leg_type_m = 1 or gs_leg_type_m = 2 then legYpos = legDistFromEdge endif if gs_leg_type_m = 3 or gs_leg_type_m = 4 then leg_a = b - 0.2 legYpos = b / 2 endif if iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_90 then rotz -45 * (gs_leg_type_m = 3 or gs_leg_type_m = 4) add -b / 2 * (gs_leg_type_m = 1 or gs_leg_type_m = 2), -b / 2, 0 else add -b / 2 * (iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_180) - b / 2 * SIN(135 / 2) * (iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_135), -b / 2 * COS(135 / 2) * (iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_135), 0 rotz 90 * (gs_leg_type_m = 3 or gs_leg_type_m = 4) endif gosub "leg" del 2
return
"leg": call "fa_desklegtyp" parameters all a = leg_a, b = leg_b, leg_h = leg_h, gs_resol = iResol, bFullPanel = 0
return
1000: roty 90 gosub 5000 del 1 return
5000: vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 base body -1 return
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS = 0.0001
TTOP_L_SHAPED = 1 TTOP_STRAIGHT = 2 TTOP_ARCHED_360 = 3 TTOP_ARCHED_180 = 4 TTOP_ARCHED_135 = 5 TTOP_ARCHED_90 = 6 TTOP_ARCHED_60 = 7 TTOP_ARCHED_45 = 8 TTOP_ARCHED_C_TOP = 9 TTOP_ARCHED_P_TOP = 10 TTOP_RECT = 11
enableLegTypes = 128 if iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_90 then enableLegTypes = (2 + 4 + 8 + 16) * bPartOfLayout + 128 if iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_135 then enableLegTypes = 2 + 4 + 128 if iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_180 then enableLegTypes = 2 + 4 + 8 + 16 * bPartOfLayout + 128 if iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_360 then enableLegTypes = 2 + 4 + 8 + 128 if iTableTopType = TTOP_ARCHED_P_TOP then enableLegTypes = 2 + 4 + 8 + 128
Symbol.Script_UI:
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
if NOT(bPartOfLayout) then
pageStartY = 5
iPageIDRoot =-1 iPageIDStyle = 1
! === Page 1 ===================================================================
UI_PAGE iPageIDStyle, iPageIDRoot, `Стиль Столешницы и Ножек`, "uiTab_Style_flat(1)"
pos_x = 0 ! start Position X Coordinate pos_y = pageStartY + 3 ! start Position Y Coordinate cell1_x = 244 ! width of 1.cell cell1_y = 255 ! height of 1.cell
ui_infield "ttyp", pos_x, pos_y, cell1_x, cell1_y, 1, 1, 9, 3, ! tableext(13).png 110, 125, 100, 100, 6, `360`, 5, `180`, 4, `135`, 3, `90`, 2, `60`, 1, `45`, 7, `С-образная`, 8, `Р-образная`, 9, `Прямоугольный`
if ttyp = `360` or ttyp = `180` or ttyp = `Р-образная` then ui_infield "gs_leg_type", cell1_x + 5, pageStartY + 3, cell1_x - 49, cell1_y, 1, "ui_legtypes(1)", 10, 5, 85, 118, 70, 90, 1, `Стиль 1`, 2, `Стиль 2`, 4, `Стиль 3`, 9, `Нет` endif
if ttyp = `135` then ui_infield "gs_leg_type", cell1_x + 5, pageStartY + 3, cell1_x - 49, cell1_y, 1, "ui_legtypes(1)", 10, 5, 85, 118, 70, 90, 1, `Стиль 1`, 2, `Стиль 2`, 9, `Нет` endif endif
Symbol.Script_VL:
! ====================================================================== ! TableTop ! ======================================================================
call "tableTops_m" parameters all enableTableTopTypes = 8 + 16 + 32 + 64 + 128 + 256 + 512 + 1024 + 2048, bPartOfLayout = 0, bCalledAsExtension = 1
! ====================================================================== ! Leg ! ======================================================================
call "fa_desklegtyp" parameters all enableLegTypes = enableLegTypes, bEnableLegbaseSurface = 1
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then lock "gs_resol" hideparameter "gs_resol" endif if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" endif
if enableLegTypes = 128 then lock "gs_leg_type", "gs_leg_type_m" hideparameter "gs_leg_type", "gs_leg_type_m" endif if iTableTopType = TTOP_RECT then lock "MSFront" hideparameter "MSFront" else lock "MSFront2", "MSRear"
hideparameter "MSFront2", "MSRear" endif

values "gs_ui_current_page" 1
